  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About low poly version</h2>Ships - Low Poly is a fully functional, low poly version of Axan Ships game<br> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Campaign<br></li><li>Free galaxy mode with spaceships<br></li><li>Free top-down mode</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Galaxy mode: Combat System</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Shield points. Shields get dented on impact<br></li><li>No health points but statuses of a ship<br></li><li>Two types of rockets<br></li><li>Two types of lasers<br></li><li>Permadeath</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Galaxy Mode: Module System</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>New modules are procedurally developed<br> </li><li>Modules get broken during battles<br></li><li>Modules get old and less reliable</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Top-Down Mode<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>scripted top-down missions</li></ul></h2></h2>",
